Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:01:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 還真晚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要在真之介面前做出很開心的樣子！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真之介！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要扔下我一個人！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬1/2 特別篇\N甦醒的記憶（下卷）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏到底是哪裏啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的怪物隨處可見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還到處佈滿陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想見到小茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了嗎 小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君才累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜小姐居然和亂馬以外的男人那麼親密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然連這裏都不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命之水不止一處嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 順著地下的水脈有好幾處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在全都乾涸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水脈出現了奇怪的變化吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:04:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不能再耽誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們趕緊去水源那裏調查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當心腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊…那種親密的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良牙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然把小茜小姐甩給了別的男人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙到底在想什麼……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 礙人的豬！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一種奇怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重的妖氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然那傢伙已經甦醒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護水源的魔物……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯……P仔！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會在這裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜親手做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 看上去很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我很有信心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎……怎麼會？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 一定是水的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個壽司用生命之水來做的話……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然會覺得小茜做的東西難吃……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定是身體哪裏不對勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 你好不容易做的……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這樣的……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦……停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裏哭出來的話……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會讓真之介君更不安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚飯我會全部都吃光的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的早中晚三餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後的每一天每一天……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一輩子都吃小茜做的飯菜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我……喜歡小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜……你討厭我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不討厭……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然不討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你已經有了這樣的打算\N我也不是不通情理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是至少把理由告訴我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把為什麼要和他交往的理由說個清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼可以說出口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君馬上就要……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣做不是在為難小茜嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要妨礙我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣的話我不想說第二遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要動手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不像這森林裏的動物那樣乖巧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜……？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你明白……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打攪你了…小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命之水的源頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是生命之水的源頭……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼快！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？怎麼了？？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快躲到那條巖縫中去！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良牙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個怪物是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是這森林的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是傳說中的魔物八歧大蛇！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:12:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泉水的變化就是它幹的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已經喝了生命之水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不……不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命之水果然已經慢慢變得無效了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了生命之水外沒有辦法救真之介君了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八歧大蛇身上長了一種很神奇的苔蘚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種苔蘚的精華溶入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就產生了生命之水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼說只要拿到那種苔蘚……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什……你想幹什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會救真之介君的命的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全都聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快要死了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋打算怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道想這樣放棄小茜小姐不管嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與你無關吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確實是被小茜小姐甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直看著的我可以說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜小姐很喜歡那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論小茜小姐喜歡誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這種情感都不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是死我也要守護著小茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜小姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有八歧大蛇的苔蘚……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著我 真之介君！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼讓小茜小姐一個人去？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等……等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是同伴起內訌的時候！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰和你是同伴啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 說不定真的是同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有勝算對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不能讓小茜一個人去做危險的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八歧大蛇最喜歡女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到女人就會馬上衝過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反過來對男人就一點興趣都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！來吧！！八歧大蛇！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最喜歡的性感美女軍團來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八歧大蛇看見女人興奮起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼覺得它好像很生氣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我多心了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這個樣子被小茜小姐看見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就……去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好！小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來就像個英勇的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人是絕對不會被吃掉的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是不吃我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是要殺掉我們啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不高明的偽裝反而激怒了八歧大蛇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？怎麼會這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明偽裝成這麼性感的女人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！這和之前商定的完全不同啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論小茜小姐喜歡誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這種情感都不會改變……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會改變！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我豁出去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜是我的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會保護好她的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的女孩子在這裏喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎過來喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍霍霍霍霍 來抓我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險啊 亂馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 輕鬆解決！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本找不到生命之苔！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能！八歧大蛇的七個頭明明都在這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,……七個？？！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是……？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第八個頭居然會在這裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！就叫它大頭八歧大蛇！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候了還管名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八歧大蛇已經聞到小茜身上女人的氣味了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊……那是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苔蘚！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就往水裏沉下去了嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬 不是你想的那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君是我的救命恩人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他為了救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的……好想把實情告訴你……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救了我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是亂來啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就給你塗生命之苔！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇……真之介你終於得救啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了啊 真之介君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜就拜託給你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:21:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你們兩個不是八歧大蛇的對手！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在快帶小茜離開！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.11,0:21:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨！女人在這裏喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去會被吃掉的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺！沒有什麼好辦法了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！那是……？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個不是八歧大蛇的天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說中的一角麝鼠的角\N所做的角笛嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一角……麝鼠？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我們家代代相傳\N用以對付八歧大蛇的密寶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:21:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會在小茜你的手裏？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快點回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個角笛是護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹著它快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我用一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.73,0:22:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去救亂馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的……未婚夫！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊來！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比較可口喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂……笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話……哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.54,0:22:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來 小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.44,0:22:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.85,0:23:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快吹角笛！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.45,0:23:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜小姐吹角笛的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迴盪在整個流幻澤上空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大頭八歧大蛇一下子就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的心都平靜了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:23:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.15,0:24:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.45,0:24:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介的傷治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.36,0:24:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就可以恢復過往的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.76,0:24:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.86,0:24:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和真之介是這座森林的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.16,0:24:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.96,0:24:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有半句怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.66,0:24:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是老朋友了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.46,0:24:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見！多保重啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.76,0:24:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.66,0:24:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.67,0:24:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終還是沒能向你表白……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.87,0:25:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的初戀……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.07,0:25:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這小子……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.27,0:25:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然忘記已經表白過了……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.67,0:25:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.67,0:25:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.97,0:25:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在害羞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.07,0:25:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 亂馬

